            <title>[CASSANDRA-5030] IndexHelper.IndexFor call throws AOB exception when passing multiple slices</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-5030</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While testing multiple slices I&apos;m seeing some exceptions when a slice hits the end of an index.&lt;/p&gt;

